text: Crowded during meal time. Zi char, carrot cake, wonton noodle and economic vegetables rice stall is worth exploring. Wonton Noodle is quite nostalgic the old school version and carrot cake white is great.

Try the carrot cake over here. the old uncle haven't lost his touch. very tasty. order the black one. you can taste the sweet sauce and the correct blend of chilli. Tasty!
